Baobab Microfinance Bank has launched a mobile App to enable its customers to have easy access to their funds and carry out seamless transactions. The mobile App named ‘MyBaobab’ built on cutting-edge technology, with ease of usage will offer customers a new banking experience. The Managing Director/Chief Executive Officer of the Bank, Dr Kazeem Olarewanju said  the launch of the App aims to ensure that customers have access to their funds to carry out transactions while keeping safe at all times. He disclosed that customers who use the new mobile App till the middle of February will be offered free transfer fees, adding that the mobile App was developed to suit customers’ lifestyles and meet their financial needs. Some of the unique features of the Mobile App include Bank to Bank transfers, Taka loan applications and loan repayment management among others; as the App allows customers to easily access their accounts with their smartphones.